ually or automatically activated.', 'RELATED': [], 'FAMILY': 'Physical And Environmental Protection', 'STATEMENTS': [{'NAME': 'PE-11 (2)(a)', 'DESCRIPTION': 'Self-contained;', 'STATEMENTS': [], 'extended_description': 'PE-11 (2)(a): Self-contained;'}, {'NAME': 'PE-11 (2)(b)', 'DESCRIPTION': 'Not reliant on external power generation; and', 'STATEMENTS': [], 'extended_description': 'PE-11 (2)(b): Not reliant on external power generation; and'}, {'NAME': 'PE-11 (2)(c)', 'DESCRIPTION': 'Capable of maintaining [Selection: minimally required operational capability; full operational capability] in the event of an extended loss of the primary power source.', 'STATEMENTS': [], 'extended_description': 'PE-11 (2)(c): Capable of maintaining [Selection: minimally required operational capability; full operational capability] in the event of an extended loss of the primary power source.'}], 'extended_description': 'The organization provides a long-term alternate power supply for the information system that is:
